N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 763.1 - General

State Regulations

This Part establishes minimum requirements and operating
standards for certified home health agencies, long term home health care
programs and AIDS home care programs. For the purposes of this Part, these
entities shall be referred to as "agency" unless the regulation specifies
otherwise. Notes
